text: Yang Hong (; born 8 September 1971) is a Chinese rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of China Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
